name: She Got Game
description: Whether they're rocking it out on their home consoles or portable gaming devices, designing the next hit RPG or competing in the Major League Gaming Championship, women are building a gaming world of their own. And yet their interests and achievements are still largely under-represented. We're interested in examining how gaming fits into women's lives socially and professionally.
